<body><page page_number="1" transcanno_page_id="2241"><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1537052834766"><div>Im Jahre <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1537052187471" tran_correction_original="1928">1940</tran_word_correction_id25> gab es eine Familie mit</div><div>einen <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="jÃ¼dischen" tagcode="1537052197974">Judischen</orth_error_id12> Vater <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537052232356" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">der sich</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_insertion_id9 class="medium-tran_word_insertion_id9" tagcode="1537052235822">mit</tran_word_insertion_id9> seiner Frau</div><div>und seiner Tochter. Sobald die Soldaten</div><div>in das Haus kamen um dem Vater Israel</div><div><tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537052288412" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">mit</tran_word_deletion_id8> zu bedrohen kam <tran_word_insertion_id9 class="medium-tran_word_insertion_id9" tagcode="1537052407860">auch</tran_word_insertion_id9> seine Familie mit <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1537052417590" tran_correction_original="ihnen">ihn</tran_word_correction_id25>.</div><div>Als sie in dem Bahnhof ankamen um dort mit</div><div>den Zug in das <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Konzentrationslager" tagcode="1537052567001">Konzentraktionslager</orth_error_id12> zu fahren.</div><div>Dort sahen sie viel Juden und verstanden,</div><div>dass <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="im" tagcode="1537052591002">ihm</orth_error_id12> Lager fahren. Israel begannsich mit</div><div>der Tochter sich zu verabschieden, da <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537052603080" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">er</tran_word_deletion_id8> der Zug</div><div>starten <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1537052778783" tran_correction_original="mussten">musste</tran_word_correction_id25>. <tran_word_insertion_id9 class="medium-tran_word_insertion_id9" tagcode="1537052786990">Dann begann seine Frau zu weinen und</tran_word_insertion_id9> Danach <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1537052800562" tran_correction_original="b">verabschiedete</tran_word_correction_id25> er</div><div>sich mit seiner Frau <tran_unreadable_id17 class="medium-tran_unreadable_id17" tagcode="1537052807941"><tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537052811469" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">*</tran_word_deletion_id8></tran_unreadable_id17> und sagte ihr: "<orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Pass" tagcode="1537052818308">Pas</orth_error_id12> auf</div><div>Ister auf, und gab ihr einKuss. Dann stieg</div><div>der Vater in dem Zug ein und Ister <tran_word_correction_id25 class="medium-tran_word_correction_id25" tagcode="1537052834765" tran_correction_original="h*bte">hebte</tran_word_correction_id25></div><div>die Hand von Israel dann begann der Zug und</div><div>langsam begann sich die Hand zu rutschen.</div><div>Und so ging der Zug weg.</div></paragraph></page></body>
